message: Dear Bob, I'm excited to offer you our premium product, which I believe would greatly benefit your needs and endeavors. Given its exceptional value and quality, we're confident it's worth more than what it costs to acquire. Considering its intrinsic worth and the benefits it offers, I propose a price of $9,500 for this product. This offer not only ensures you receive a high-quality item at a reasonable price but also allows us to maintain a fair profit margin. We value your consideration and hope to facilitate a transaction that benefits both parties.
